<br>
That's a reasonable rule of thumb, but it only works when you have comparable weapons. A 17/28 weapon is so much better than a 7/18 weapon that they are not in the same league.<br>
<br>
Your damage bonus at 45 is 6 (7 at 46), so, in your primary hand, the SoS is ((17*2)+6)/28 = 1.43 and the FoR is ((7*2)+6)/18 = 1.11.<br>
<br>
Besides, Fist of Rock is a HTH weapon and HTH is capped at 225 in the high 40s versus 240 for 1HB. Just get another SoS and you'll be all set. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=71792 target=_blank>Scalia</a> /  <a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=71783 target =_blank>Gluon</a> on E'ci</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=11844.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showNextMessage?topicID=11844.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11844.topic&index=0><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.emailToFriend?topicID=11844.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.threadControl?topicID=11844.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11844.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11844.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="